              "free_text": [
                " The quoted errors in the cross sections",
                "include:",
                " * uncertainties in the beam intensities,",
                " * uncertainties in target weights,",
                " * uncertainties in counting efficiencies,",
                " * uncertainties in counting statistics,",
                " * uncertainties in conversion coefficients,",
                " * uncertainties in decay branching ratios and",
                "   half-life values.",
                "The total error in the cross section are thought to",
                "be 15% or less.",
                "The errors in the deuteron energies represent the",
                "uncertainty in the incident beam energy, compounded by",
                "the estimated energy spread during degradation in the",
                "stacks."
